# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Vaulter AI Property Intelligence System
# Environment Variables — Example File
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
#   1. Copy this file to your confidentials/ folder
#   2. Rename it to .env (remove the .example)
#   3. Fill in your actual values below
#   4. NEVER commit the real .env to GitHub
#
# File location:
#   Windows : C:\Users\YashuLanki\Vaulter AI\confidentials\.env
#   Mac     : <project_root>/confidentials/.env
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════


# ── Anthropic / Claude API ────────────────────────────────────────
# Get this from: https://console.anthropic.com → API Keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here


# ── Microsoft Outlook / Graph API ────────────────────────────────
# Get these from: portal.azure.com → App registrations
OUTLOOK_CLIENT_ID=your-application-id-here
OUTLOOK_TENANT_ID=your-directory-tenant-id-here
OUTLOOK_CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret-value-here


# ── MCP Server Security ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Secret key that protects your MCP server endpoint.
MCP_API_KEY=your-random-secret-key-here


# ── Google Place API Key ───────────────────────────────────────────
GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=your-random-secret-key-here
